Summary:        A Digital Camera Library
License:        LGPL-2.1-or-later
Group:          Hardware/Camera
Version:        2.5.27
Release:        0
Source0:        https://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/gphoto/libgphoto/%version/%name-%version.tar.xz
